{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","data":{"body":"CORRECTION to the epic's Context (from task 0730's live probe): the rising floor DOES drop findings on remediation-eligible rounds - the earlier '0 novelty drops ever' figure was a scan artifact (JSON-string-encoded sidecar data fields were silently skipped). Corrected: 33/35 eligible post-flip reviews narrowed with ~111 floored findings, and the live scorer probe (34 pairs, 541 findings) shows 0% errors and perfect carryover discrimination. UNCHANGED: 240 reviews were ineligible because BLOCK verdicts never sign, so the floor still never engages in BLOCK loops - story a850's motivation stands on that finding alone."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1784099231122635001,"uuid":"f1d436e5-edb6-4be7-b1fb-2ed0c991c4e6"}